        <item>
            <title>劳工处将推「职安程式」新版，可匿名举报工业安全问题</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/20/alert-from-larbour-department/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=alert-from-larbour-department</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/20/alert-from-larbour-department/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 08:33:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[劳工处]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1220595</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>劳工处表示，最快将于今年首季推出新版本的应用程式，加入严重或致命工业意外发出的「职安警示」、「职安警示」动画讲解，以及举报功能，让用家可以用匿名形式投诉工业安全问题。</p><p>现时劳工处在发生严重或致命工业意外后，会在官方网站、应用程式及透过电邮发出现「职安警示」，提醒业界采取安全措施，以免再次发生同类型意外。</p><p>目前劳工处「职安警示」网上版可见，劳工处会提供意外日期、地点及意外摘要。同时劳工处会提供建议予拥有人、东主及雇主。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220717" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240220133220-431x580.jpg" alt="" width="431" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240220133220-431x580.jpg 431w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240220133220.jpg 669w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 431px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220718" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240220133236-431x580.jpg" alt="" width="431" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240220133236-431x580.jpg 431w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240220133236.jpg 669w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 431px" /></p><p>劳工处官方网站亦有职安警示动画。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220720" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240220134157-601x580.jpg" alt="" width="601" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240220134157-601x580.jpg 601w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240220134157.jpg 932w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 601px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220719" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire-1708407543-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire-1708407543-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire-1708407543.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲劳工处有关「挖掘机的安全操作」的动画影片</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220722" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲劳工处有关「悬空式竹棚架拆卸」的动画影片</p><div class="items_content"><div class="itemBody"><div class="itemFullText">劳工处副处长冯浩贤接受港台专访时透露，最快今年第一季会提升「职安警示」内容及发放方式。劳工处已开始试行新应用程式。据港台引述劳工处表示，根据职安健法例，通常处方不会会公开调查结果，而工业伤亡权益会认为，政府应该公开全部严重职场意外调查结果，使业界可避免再次发生同类型惨案。</div></div></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/news/work_safety_alert.htm">劳工处</a>、<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1741019-20240220.htm">RTHK</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/20/alert-from-larbour-department/life-tech/smartcity/">劳工处将推「职安程式」新版，可匿名举报工业安全问题</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/20/alert-from-larbour-department/life-tech/smartcity/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
